title: Gossip Princess
overview: To find her way home, Liang Hong must collect all five glass beads, but she accidentally "messes with" five men. Liang Hong has been repeatedly "forced to marry", which not only causes her to get into scandals but also makes her a player from a person who's never been in a relationship before. Then she becomes a female version of "Wei Xiaobao", who's got seven wives, in Jiankang City. She was going to run away after the scam, but she's caught up in a conspiracy...
